FBIS3-8387 "dreeu046__a94002" FBIS-EEU-94-046-A Document Type:Daily Report 9 March 1994 ANNEX Bulgaria Berov Hospitalized After `Heart Failure' AU0803144194 Sofia BTA in English 1432 GMT 8 Mar 94 AU0803144194 Sofia BTA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Sofia, March 8 (BTA) -- Prime Minister Lyuben Berov had a heart failure at 2 AM [0000 GMT] on March 8, the Cabinet Press Office said today. He was taken to the Lozenets Hospital of the Military Medical Academy in Sofia. A team held consultation and placed Prof. Berov under medical treatment.
